* &quot;The Power of Glamour: Longing and the Art of Visual Persuasion&quot;, Simon &amp; Schuster, November 5, 2013 ()
* &quot;The Fabric of Civilization: How Textiles Made the World&quot;, Basic Books, November 10, 2020 ()

