<doc id="403964" wikidata="Q5115306" url="?curid=403964" title="Chucho Avellanet">
<text>Armando Hipólito Avellanet González, nicknamed &quot;Chucho&quot;, is a Puerto Rican singer and comedic actor of Spanish-Catalan descent. Avellanet was involved with the Nueva ola movement in the 1960s.

